codes.body:
A bicyclist upon the roadway or upon any public path set aside for the use of bicycles shall give hand and arm signals in the following manner:
<br />1. Left turn, left hand and arm extended horizontally;
<br />2. Right turn, left hand and arm extended upward, or right hand and arm extended horizontally;
<br />3. Stop or decrease speed, left or right hand and arm extended downward.
